snippet.title: CARROT with EGG | Unique Carrot and Egg Recipe Cooking in Village | Chicken Inside Scrambled Omelet
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook the scrambled omelette recipe with using eggs and carrots. Usually, the Omelette recipe is one of the breakfast recipe, but we made it for full meals heaven. 

We add more flavor to omelette by using full chickens. We finally taste the scrambled omelette with chicken and mutton curry. The taste is the fullest!

Tere Bin Episode 07 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 18th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.title: Bakra Nahi Majnu Halaal - Part 2 : Full On Farziwada - Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Skkily Ludo App From 
https://bit.ly/Amit-bhadana

REFERRAL CODE - AMIT100


Jab aag lagi hai to dhamaka to ho kar rahega. Hamare Majnu ne le lie hain bade wala panga. 2 ladkiyon ko date toh bahut log karte hain lekin hamara hero 2 sagi behnon se pyar kar baitha hani. Lalach buri bala hain Rinku na Raveena se breakup karna chahata hai aur na hi Sangeeta ko ta-ta bye-bye, aur ab vo galti se pahunch gaya hain dono ke ghar jahan bas phootne hi wala hai uska bhaanda. Kya hoga aage isi baat ka hai sabko intezaar. Kya Sangeeta aur Raveena mil kar karengi Rinku ko halal ya unke papa karenge hamare Majnu ka kaam tamaam? Kya hoga is love story ka end? Ye sab pata chalega is part mein. To sab mil kar hamare Majnu ke lie prarthna karo aur poore parivaar family ke sath dekho ye kamaal dhamaal story. Dhnyaawad :)

Today on 18 January,2023 I am presenting the video of shattila ekadashi vrat katha. Shattila ekadashi comes on ekadashi of magh maas krishna pakash. Magh Maas Krishna Paksha Ekadashi is known as shattila ekadashi. Lets watch video of Shattila Ekadashi ki Kahani, Shattila Ekadashi ki Katha, Shattila ekadashi vrat Katha, Shattila ekadashi vrat ki katha, shattila ekadashi pooja. People pray to Lord Vishnu on the auspicious day of Shattila Ekadashi.  In the video of Shattila Ekadashi Katha, One old lady got everything after performing shattila ekadashi vrat and shattila ekadashi puja vidhi. 
Shatila Ekadashi will be celebrated on 18 January 2023, Friday.
in second shattila ekadashi katha, one woodcutter had changed his life by performing shattila ekadashi vrat. He and his wife both followed shattila ekadashi puja vidhi and performed shattila ekadashi vrat and listened shattila ekadashi ki kahani. after that, they became honorable people of their village. 
Jai shri Hari vishnu bhagwan

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

snippet.description:
Here is The #Samantha's #MallikaMallika Lyrical Song From #Shaakuntalam Movie, Sung By Ramya Behara, Music By Mani Sharma, Lyrics are Penned By Chaitanya Prasad & Directed By Gunasekhar.

https://youtube.com/TipsTelugu

Song Details : 
Song Name : Mallika Mallika 
Singer : Ramya Behara
Music Director: Mani Sharma 
Lyricist: Chaitanya Prasad 

Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa‚Äôs Sanskrit play ‚ÄòAbhijnana Shakuntalam‚Äô is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant‚Äôs Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

Farq Episode 24 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 17th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

About The Show

The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

In this video, Abhi and Niyu discuss RBI's Special Vostro Account plan to make Rupee an International currency. Now NRIs will be able to use UPI to transfer money in 10 countries. This is a great start to 2023 as it will slowly make Indian technology international. But apart from UPI, we can even make our Rupee an international currency. What are the challenges and what is the plan? We discuss in this explainer video.

The Pandeys decide to reveal the truth about Bihaan to Thapki and cure him with her help. Watching things get out of hand, Shraddha tortures Bihaan by reminding him of his traumatic past when he was separated from Thapki. Will this make his situation worse?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: ‡§∏‡§®‡•Ä ‡§¶‡•á‡§ì‡§≤ ‡§®‡•á ‡§Ö‡§Æ‡•É‡§§‡§æ ‡§∏‡§ø‡§Ç‡§π ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§¶‡•Ä '‡§ï‡§ø‡§∏' ‡§ï‡•Ä ‡§∏‡•õ‡§æ - Betaab - Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Shammi Kapoor
snippet.description:
Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

This film is a love story of two youngsters who fall in love despite the status gaps between their families. Sunny, is a young, poor and happy guy who lives with his mother Sumitra in his home-made town farm. Formerly, his father Avenash had been a big businessman, but he went bankrupt. For this reason, he killed himself. Avenash was close friends with Sardar Dinesh Singh Girji who is one of the richest and most powerful men in the city. When Sardar reveals that Avenash has gone bankrupt, he turns his back to him. Sardar has one daughter called Roma. She is spoiled, snobbish and accustomed to having all the people who surround her beneath her. She was Sunny's childhood friend.

Now, Sardar purchases a new horse farm out of the city in the town, which is nearby Sunny's farm. When Sunny accompanies his mother to the train station, he encounters Roma after not seeing her for years. Sunny instantly recognizes her, but Roma doesn't. Consequently, they coincidentally meet each other various times on the farm. They quarrel continually, but soon she realises that he is her childhood friend and they reconstruct their childhood love.

Directed by Rahul Rawail
Written by Javed Akhtar
Produced by Bikram Singh Dahal
Starring - Shammi Kapoor, Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Nirupa Roy, Prem Chopra, Rehana

Subscribe To Shemaroo Movie in Parts: https://www.youtube.com/user/shemaroopremiumfilms?sub_confirmation=1

This film is a love story of two youngsters who fall in love despite the status gaps between their families. Sunny, is a young, poor and happy guy who lives with his mother Sumitra in his home-made town farm. Formerly, his father Avenash had been a big businessman, but he went bankrupt. For this reason, he killed himself. Avenash was close friends with Sardar Dinesh Singh Girji who is one of the richest and most powerful men in the city. When Sardar reveals that Avenash has gone bankrupt, he turns his back to him. Sardar has one daughter called Roma. She is spoiled, snobbish and accustomed to having all the people who surround her beneath her. She was Sunny's childhood friend.

Now, Sardar purchases a new horse farm out of the city in the town, which is nearby Sunny's farm. When Sunny accompanies his mother to the train station, he encounters Roma after not seeing her for years. Sunny instantly recognizes her, but Roma doesn't. Consequently, they coincidentally meet each other various times on the farm. They quarrel continually, but soon she realises that he is her childhood friend and they reconstruct their childhood love.

Directed by Rahul Rawail
Written by Javed Akhtar
Produced by Bikram Singh Dahal
Starring - Shammi Kapoor, Sunny Deol, Amrita Singh, Nirupa Roy, Prem Chopra, Rehana
Cinematography Manmohan Singh
Music by Rahul Dev Burman

snippet.description:
Watch the Preview of the bengali serial "Nayantara" which airs on Sun Bangla TV.
  
  Watch all Sun Bangla Full episodes FREE on SUN NXT App. Offer Valid only in India and Bangladesh, till 31st January 
  Download here: 
  Android - http://bit.ly/SunNxtAdroid 
  iOS: India - http://bit.ly/sunNXT 
  Watch on the web - https://www.sunnxt.com/
  
  Nayantara: After 30 years of marriage, Adidev (Gourab Mondal) and Averi (Payal De) are about to experience parenthood with the birth of their first child. The doctor warns Avery that she might face life threatening complications if she decides to go ahead with the child birth. Averi does not tell Adidev about this because she wants to give him the happiness of fatherhood and be a mother herself. On the other hand, Avery means the world to Adidev, so he will definitely chose her life over the child. Avery gives birth to Tara (Hiya Mukherjee). Avery dies within a few minutes of Tara√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢s birth. The doctor informs Adidev that he had warned Avery but she did not listen. Adidev, who was already devastated by his wife's death, comes to know that the Income Tax Department had raided his office. Adidev starts to believe that Tara is the source of the misfortune in his life and hatred grows in his heart for Tara. On the other hand, Adidev's second wife Madhuja (Swarnakamal) loves Tara more than her own daughter Preeti. But Adideb can√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢t tolerate that either. Tara's only wish, will she ever get his father's affection?
  
  SUBSCRIBE to Sun Bangla YouTube channel - http://bit.ly/2kviBbJ

Adidev starts to believe that Tara is the source of the misfortune in his life and hatred grows in his heart for Tara. On the other hand, Adidev's second wife Madhuja (Swarnakamal) loves Tara more than her own daughter Preeti. But Adideb can√¢‚Ç¨‚Ñ¢t tolerate that either. Tara's only wish, will she ever get his father's affection?

snippet.title: DAMaN (In Hindi) Official Trailer | Babushaan Mohanty, Dipanwit D | In Cinemas 3rd February 2023
snippet.description:
In 2015, a young doctor, Dr. Siddharth Mohanty, who has just completed his MBBS from a government medical college, is posted  to a back of beyond tribal area in the Malkangiri district. Janbai PHC has 151 villages under it, is  infamous for its Naxal dominance and doesn't even boast of the most basic facilities. 
Dr. Siddharth Mohanty arrives reluctantly, wanting to quit at the earliest. But fate wills otherwise.  Daman is the story of 151 villages and one doctor to control the spread of malaria, the tussle between superstition and medical science. 

Presenting you the official trailer of DAMaN in Hindi.

Thapki discovers that Bihaan is hiding in Bani's room. What will be her reaction to seeing him? Earlier, Bani manipulates Thapki into spending some valuable time with Bihaan and Tina. 

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3669 - 16 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3669: Bawri Vapas Aagayi
--------------------------------------------------------
Bawri arrives in Gokuldham and surprises everyone. Bagha breaks down when he sees his love, Bawri. Bawri is bombarded with inquiries about her sudden disappearance. She explains to everyone that everything happened because of a minor misunderstanding. Her hair color was messed up by a salon called "Baby," and instead of texting them, she texted Bagha. In any case, everyone is relieved that Bagha and Bawri are reunited. Bhide suggests to Madhavi that Bawri's return may be a problem disguised as an opportunity. Nattu Kaka and Bagha later go missing. Keep an eye out!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3669, 16 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

------------

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe.

snippet.description:
Episode 712: Maddam Sir ‡§®‡•á Billu ‡§î‡§∞ Cheetah ‡§ï‡•ã ‡§¶‡§ø‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§á‡§∏ Crocodile ‡§ï‡•Ä Responsibilty 
--------------------------------------------
Maddam Sir and her team rescue a gigantic crocodile while investigating a case of animal skin trafficking. Suddenly, Maddam Sir hears a mass protest outside her police station claiming that she has been involved in this racket. Initially, they locked up the crocodile inside the prison but it somehow escapes. Haseena Mallick asks Billu Champat and Cheetah Chaturvedi to find out about the crocodile. Will Billu and Cheetah be able to handle such a creature? Stay tuned!

Show Name ‚Äì Maddam Sir
Star Cast ‚Äì  Gulki Joshi, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Episode No ‚Äì 712
Produced By ‚Äì  Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir  #‡§Æ‡•à‡§°‡•ç‡§°‡§Æ‡§∏‡§∞ #SAB

Click here to Subscribe to SAB TV Channel: 
https://www.youtube.com/user/sabtv?sub_confirmation=1

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama madam and comedy.

Click here to watch the full episode of Maddam Sir:
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7b5cZhAf5s-a8BZAoiGePqE

snippet.title: Kanuma Special Ratham muggulu designsüå∫Beautiful Chariot rangoli & kolam
snippet.description:
Kanuma Special Ratham muggulu designsüå∫Beautiful Chariot rangoli & kolam.
Kolam or muggu is a ancient art form of India which is very popular.
Kolam is also called as Rangoli in parts of India.
women create different kolam or rangoli designs infront of the doorstep in the early morning
taking ideas from the nature like flowers,deepams,diyas,animals like elephants,cows, fruits, birds likev peacock and swan etc.
In Andhra pradesh and Telangana, kolam designs are called muggulu.
Rangoli or kolam designs are drawn with dots like 5 dots, 6 dots and so on and without dots also (freehand rangoli).
People celebrate festivals like Diwali,Sankranthi (Pongal), Ganesh Chathurthi,Dasara( Vijaya dasami) by drawing different 
creative Kolam or rangoli designs with different colors and flowers in fornt of their houses.
People draw Beautiful special kolams on Friday to get the blessings of Godess Lakshmi.
Designs vary from easy rangoli for beginners to difficult levels for professionals.
#rangoli #kolam #muggulu
